INDLELA owesifazane agqoke ngayo kayisho ukuthi kumele adlwengulwe! Ngeledlule kube nempikiswano ezinkundleni ezahlukahlukene kuphikiswana ngokuthi indlela owesifazane agqoke ngayo iyaholela yini ekutheni agcine eyisisulu sokudlwengulwa. Le mpikiswano isuswe yisithombe esibe ngundabuzekwayo sezintokazi ezimbili ebezishaye ezincane eziveza amathanga zisendaweni yokuzithokozisa yaseMlaza, eYadini.Ngemuva kokuvela kwalesi sithombe, umsakazi woKhozi FM uKhathide Tshath ugodo Ngobe ubhale kuFacebook egxeka lezi zintokazi waze wathi ukugqoka kwazo ziveze amathanga kwenza abesilisa bacabange umbhede kuphela.Uze wathi ngeke baze bawuthole nomshado ngakho belu ukugqoka kanje.UTshatha uxolisile ngokuphawula kanje obekungenasidingo kepha okutatulule kwagqamisa isihlava sokuthi kusekhona abantu abangakuqondi ukuthi indlela owesifazane agqoke ngayo kayisho neze ukuthi kumele adlwengulwe.Sekukade kuba nemikhankaso ezama ukufundisa nokuqwashisa ngesihlava sokudlwengulwa kwabesifazane nezingane.Enye yezinto ezikhulunywayo kule mikhankaso ngukuthi ukugqoka akusho lutho njengoba kukhona abadlwengula izingane nezaguga.Yingakho kuphoxa ukuthi kukhona abebegxeka lezi zintokazi ebeziseYadini ngokukhinda bethi zizibizela ukudlwengulwa.Isigameko sowesifazane owayegqoke isigqebhe wathunazwa isithunzi erenki eseNoord, eGoli, ngesinye ezagqamisa umkhankaso wokuthi indlela owesifazane agqoke ngayo kayisho ukuthi kumele adlwengulwe noma ehliswe isithunzi.Kusobala ukuthi kumele iqhubeke futhi iqine imikhankaso yokugxisha lokhu emakhanda yikhona uzophela lo mqondo omubi wokuthi owesifazane uzibizela ukudlwengulwa ngendlela agqoke ngayo.Izinhlangano ezilwa nokuhlukunyezwa nokudlwengulwa kwabesifazane nezinhlaka zikahulumeni kumele zibukisise le mpikiswano equbuke ezinkundleni ebese ziqhamuka nezinhlelo nemikhankaso yokufundisa umphakathi ngokuthi indlela owesifazane agqoke ngayo kayisho ukuthi kumele adlwengulwe!